<p>You really shouldn't be playing enchanter if you're going to whine so much.  I for one am glad they nerfed chanters charm, because that's all I used to do was charm and neva realized the potential of my class in a group.  OOW came out with the intentions that no class should be able to solo the good portion of it.  So it'd actually take a little work to get the good stuff, instead of charming a high lvl mob and killing a named within seconds.  There is not too many spots in oow where and class can solo and get goodxp, plus drops all the time.  Sure a necro can kite mobs in a few areas, and maybe get a ultra rare drop in a month of playtime.  But you don't see them farming gear on their own.  You also don't see bards running around swarm kiting these zones, getting massive xp and loot.  This was a way to make every class to stop and think of ways to work together with the people around you and take out harder mobs that drops better gear. To dis rune, shows that you know nothing about enchanters.  An enchanter rune is his hp that he can heal ova and ova.  With quickbuff you can increase your rune cast by half which is like 2.5 seconds I believe.  On the majority of mobs this means you can chain rune and maybe never even get hit, depending on your defensive and stability.  Also if you have your epic 1.5 you can use this rune free of mana! (gosh) And I guess they didnt think of us when they gave us a low resist mez to save us from the ungodly aggro you get when mez resists, or maybe the low resist slow when you're trying to slow and it seems like the resist has more aggro then when they actually slow themselves.  To says enchanters aren't needed anymore is completely ignorant, have you ever been to a raid without enchanters?  <br /> <br />To end my post I would like to say you are a complete idiot and we don't want you in our enchanter community anyway, so please stay away.</p>
